snippet.title: Let's Play Super Mario War Part 1
snippet.description:
First part of my Let's Play of Hobojoe285's World in Super Mario War. Hobojoe made all the levels and even the characters used in this video (Ninja and 2 different Dragoons).

I would like to thank him again for all the effort he put into this, and once again link you guys to his channel http://www.youtube.com/user/hobojoe285

He also did an LP of his world, although he is much more skilled at this game than me.

You can download this version of the game at http://smw.supersanctuary.net/site/index.php?dl

And if you want these levels/characters PM Hobojoe285.
